Writer: Andrew Stanton (original story by), Andrew Stanton (screenplay by), Victoria Strouse (screenplay by), Bob Peterson (additional screenplay material by), Angus MacLane (additional story material by)
Title: Finding Dory
Actors: Ellen DeGeneres, Albert Brooks, Ed O'Neill, Kaitlin Olson
Plot: The friendly but forgetful blue tang fish, Dory, begins a search for her long-lost parents, and everyone learns a few things about the real meaning of family along the way.
Awards: Nominated for 1 BAFTA Film Award. Another 15 wins & 42 nominations.
